metadata.name: BEREHYNIA
metadata.description:
BEREHYNIA is a Goddess of Protection in Ukrainian Folklore. 
She is the Guardian of Ukrainian culture and identity, the Mother of all living things, a Protectoress of home and family.
On 24 February russia attacked Ukraine and started the most pointless inhumane and barbaric war against my country and something they can’t tolerate: our freedom and independence. 

BEREHYNIA represents all of us and how we will win this war and rise above.

100% of proceeds will go to the Ukraine’s official ETH donation address.
